import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Tidyflow — clean digital tools to help you get organized.">
  <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">About Tidyflow</h1>

  <div class="post-content">
    <p>We believe getting organized shouldn't be complicated.</p>

    <p>Tidyflow creates clean, minimal digital tools — starting with Notion templates — that help you take control of your time, money, and goals. Every product is designed with one principle in mind: <strong>just open and start using</strong>.</p>

    <p>No complicated formulas. No overwhelming features. No 50-page setup guides. Just simple tools that work.</p>

    <h2>What We Make</h2>
    <p>We focus on Notion templates for personal productivity: budget trackers, habit trackers, project managers, and more. Each template comes with sample data so you can see exactly how it works before customizing it for yourself.</p>

    <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
    <p>The best system is the one you actually use. That's why we obsess over simplicity. If a template needs a tutorial to understand, it's too complicated.</p>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <h3>Browse Our Templates</h3>
      <p>Find the right tool to help you get organized.</p>
      <a href="/products" class="cta-button">View Products →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
